The '''Group Commander Citation''' was an award given to [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]].

[[Ace Azzameen/Legends|Ace Azzameen]] was awarded the Group Commander Citation for his role in taking down the Imperial research facility responsible for the TIE Experimental Project.

